        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Open and Responsive Government Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill limits the extent to which federal agencies may exempt information from requests to disclose agency records under the Freedom of Information Act, including prohibiting the withholding of a portion of an otherwise responsive record on the basis that the portion is nonresponsive.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
